WEBVTT

01:39.509 --> 01:43.570
[Road to Success]

01:44.600 --> 01:47.810
[Episode 5]

01:59.350 --> 02:00.280
Outdoor sports—

02:00.280 --> 02:01.310
cycling.

02:01.950 --> 02:03.870
Today's goal is to burn 800 kcal.

02:04.350 --> 02:05.640
It should take

02:05.640 --> 02:07.170
about 2 hours and 9 minutes.

02:07.870 --> 02:09.150
That should be reasonable

02:09.150 --> 02:11.120
but not too demanding, right?

02:12.030 --> 02:14.080
Why not go all the way
and time it to the second?

02:14.080 --> 02:16.030
That's way too challenging.

02:17.360 --> 02:19.800
If you don't know how to ride a bike,

02:20.560 --> 02:22.560
you can just scoot along on one foot.

02:22.560 --> 02:23.400
Or...

02:24.280 --> 02:25.420
admit defeat.

02:26.470 --> 02:28.030
Who says I can't ride?

02:29.000 --> 02:29.840
Excuse me,

02:29.840 --> 02:30.840
show me your hand.

02:34.590 --> 02:35.470
What for?

02:39.400 --> 02:41.800
You're quite well-equipped.

02:44.030 --> 02:45.240
This sports watch

02:44.190 --> 02:46.079
[Cycling] [Average Pace]

02:45.240 --> 02:46.440
is synced to my phone.

02:46.750 --> 02:48.170
I can see your data.

02:49.630 --> 02:51.200
Let me remind you again,

02:51.910 --> 02:53.280
Ms. Lin—

02:53.280 --> 02:55.280
you can admit defeat anytime.

02:55.280 --> 02:56.120
Don't worry.

02:56.120 --> 02:56.960
In my whole life,

02:56.960 --> 02:59.620
"admit defeat" has never been
in my vocabulary.

03:09.700 --> 03:12.360
I don't know how to ride a bike at all.

03:13.770 --> 03:17.150
[Fifteen minutes later]

03:26.680 --> 03:27.980
[Cycling] [Average Pace]

03:28.329 --> 03:30.000
No movement at all.

03:31.490 --> 03:33.350
Looks like she really can't ride.

03:34.800 --> 03:36.079
A friendly reminder,

03:36.280 --> 03:37.430
Ms. Lin—

03:37.430 --> 03:38.680
time waits for no one.

03:39.360 --> 03:40.590
If you can't ride,

03:40.590 --> 03:41.790
you can admit defeat.

03:44.630 --> 03:45.470
To hell with it.

03:45.470 --> 03:46.400
I'm going for it.

03:49.030 --> 03:52.850
[Three hours later]

03:57.020 --> 03:58.810
[Cycling] [Average Pace]

03:58.650 --> 04:00.310
She learned to ride that fast?

04:03.630 --> 04:04.680
Where are you?

04:06.430 --> 04:08.030
The neighborhood park.

04:21.160 --> 04:21.800
Sister,

04:21.800 --> 04:23.430
you're still using training wheels?

04:23.430 --> 04:24.800
We stopped using those ages ago.

04:24.800 --> 04:26.760
They're my secret weapon.

04:27.560 --> 04:29.560
Pretty crafty, huh?

04:32.000 --> 04:32.630
Sister,

04:32.630 --> 04:34.120
let's race and see who's faster!

04:34.120 --> 04:35.750
Could the person in front of me,

04:35.750 --> 04:37.880
who hit it off with the kids right away,

04:38.480 --> 04:41.120
really be the malicious Spade Q?

04:48.830 --> 04:50.100
Be careful, you kids.

04:54.159 --> 04:55.650
Sister, you're too slow.

04:55.190 --> 04:57.400
♪ Two souls alike ♪

04:55.680 --> 04:58.200
How are you still this slow
with four wheels?

04:58.360 --> 05:00.680
With four wheels,
it's harder to keep everything balanced,

04:59.060 --> 05:00.940
♪ In the silent gravity ♪

05:00.680 --> 05:01.720
so I can't go fast.

05:01.720 --> 05:02.890
Come on, Sister!

05:03.220 --> 05:05.350
♪ Cure my heart ♪

05:03.560 --> 05:05.600
See? I passed you.

05:05.870 --> 05:06.960
Maybe

05:05.970 --> 05:08.640
♪ With every part of you ♪

05:07.560 --> 05:08.600
she

05:09.120 --> 05:10.390
didn't mean to do that?

05:11.120 --> 05:13.210
♪ Our words flow ♪

05:14.600 --> 05:16.830
♪ Like a gentle stream ♪

05:18.920 --> 05:21.100
♪ They glow like fireflies ♪

05:21.760 --> 05:24.280
♪ Inside of a silky dream ♪

05:26.490 --> 05:32.320
♪ We talked the whole night, breeze away ♪

05:34.300 --> 05:36.090
♪ Together we set out on a long journey ♪

05:35.800 --> 05:36.750
We won.

05:36.720 --> 05:39.780
♪ The endless journey ♪

05:36.750 --> 05:38.630
We won! We won!

05:38.630 --> 05:40.430
Congratulations.

05:40.920 --> 05:43.180
So this is what you call
"a piece of cake"?

05:43.720 --> 05:45.120
This is called cheating.

05:45.560 --> 05:46.360
What do you know?

05:46.360 --> 05:48.620
This is called strategic intelligence.

05:49.480 --> 05:52.040
You've already been riding
for 1 hour and 3 minutes,

05:52.040 --> 05:55.310
but you've only burned 120 kcal.

05:55.310 --> 05:56.040
How is that possible?

05:56.040 --> 05:57.040
Didn't you say two hours

05:57.040 --> 05:58.600
would burn 800 kcal?

05:58.600 --> 05:59.750
Your heart rate is too low.

05:59.750 --> 06:00.800
To raise it,

06:00.800 --> 06:02.600
you need to speed up or go uphill.

06:03.270 --> 06:04.800
Got it.

06:07.800 --> 06:08.920
There's nothing in this world

06:08.920 --> 06:10.950
that I can't learn!

06:21.240 --> 06:22.370
Not riding anymore?

06:22.560 --> 06:24.560
Four wheels really are unreliable.

06:25.120 --> 06:26.160
One just flew off.

06:26.720 --> 06:27.680
You fell?

06:30.070 --> 06:31.390
I have a cramp.

06:33.190 --> 06:33.920
Sit.

06:38.390 --> 06:39.450
What are you doing?

06:40.360 --> 06:41.390
Bear with it a little.

06:41.390 --> 06:42.320
It'll hurt a bit.

06:47.560 --> 06:48.560
Do you know what you're doing?

06:48.560 --> 06:51.020
Maybe I should
go find a bonesetter instead.

06:54.390 --> 06:55.040
There.

06:55.600 --> 06:56.600
Try moving it now.

07:04.130 --> 07:05.330
[Calories: 433 kcal]
[Average Heart Rate: 146 bpm]

07:07.750 --> 07:10.310
Now, you can keep riding
with a busted leg like that.

07:10.310 --> 07:11.920
Still 367 kcal to go.

07:11.920 --> 07:13.270
My leg just cramped up!

07:13.270 --> 07:15.040
Do you have any humanity left?

07:16.680 --> 07:17.390
I'm hungry.

07:17.390 --> 07:18.450
I need to eat first.

07:19.550 --> 07:21.880
I'll figure something out after I'm full.

07:23.360 --> 07:25.480
So, Ms. Lin, are you admitting defeat?

07:25.480 --> 07:27.460
That's right. I admit defeat.

07:27.830 --> 07:29.360
Even though I lost this morning,

07:29.360 --> 07:31.890
that doesn't mean
you'll win this afternoon.

07:32.040 --> 07:33.040
Just you wait.

07:34.800 --> 07:36.330
Who are you trying to scare?

07:36.920 --> 07:38.159
Trying to buy more time?

07:38.159 --> 07:38.720
Yeah.

07:38.720 --> 07:39.270
So what?

07:40.830 --> 07:41.510
We're here.

07:41.510 --> 07:42.770
It's that place ahead.

07:46.510 --> 07:48.120
How about we go somewhere else?

07:48.120 --> 07:49.070
Why?

07:49.070 --> 07:50.800
Their wontons are really good.

07:53.680 --> 07:56.190
There's still 1 minute and 45 seconds
until 12 o'clock.

07:56.190 --> 07:56.950
It's still morning,

07:56.950 --> 07:58.409
so you have to listen to me.

07:58.750 --> 08:00.830
-I'll find a better restaurant...
-Ma'am!

08:00.830 --> 08:01.680
I'm here.

08:09.120 --> 08:09.510
Found one.

08:09.510 --> 08:10.440
It's 12 o'clock.

08:10.830 --> 08:12.230
Unbelievable.

08:12.360 --> 08:14.290
Starting now, you'll listen to me.

08:14.510 --> 08:15.510
Trust me.

08:15.510 --> 08:16.720
It's really good.

08:21.830 --> 08:23.390
Here, enjoy.

08:25.270 --> 08:26.680
-Thank you.
-You're welcome.

08:26.680 --> 08:28.210
-Thanks.
-You're welcome.

08:35.669 --> 08:37.070
You don't eat coriander?

08:52.380 --> 08:53.230
[Loves spicy food; hates coriander]

08:53.250 --> 08:54.770
[Bad at sports; can't ride a bike]

08:56.440 --> 08:57.660
She likes spicy food

08:58.300 --> 08:59.570
and hates coriander.

09:05.910 --> 09:07.030
This is so good.

09:09.510 --> 09:10.360
Do you want some?

09:10.360 --> 09:11.510
No, thanks.

09:11.960 --> 09:14.420
A grown man,
but you can't handle spicy food?

09:14.480 --> 09:15.320
So weak.

09:15.840 --> 09:17.040
Let me trick him a bit.

09:18.080 --> 09:20.340
Have you ever heard of drinking wontons?

09:21.390 --> 09:23.670
For wontons like these, with thin wrappers
and just a little filling,

09:23.670 --> 09:25.730
you can just drink them with the soup.

09:29.150 --> 09:29.870
Won't that

09:30.910 --> 09:32.150
burn her mouth?

09:35.790 --> 09:36.480
Try it.

09:41.120 --> 09:42.320
Look closely.

09:42.320 --> 09:43.840
It's after 12 o'clock now.

09:43.840 --> 09:45.170
You have to listen to me.

09:46.080 --> 09:48.120
Finally, it's my turn to call the shots.

09:48.120 --> 09:49.750
First, a street food stall,

09:49.750 --> 09:51.900
and now she wants me to drink wontons.

09:52.440 --> 09:53.790
Is she messing with me?

09:59.080 --> 09:59.960
It's so hot.

09:59.960 --> 10:01.290
Got you.

10:02.510 --> 10:03.500
Is it good?

10:04.630 --> 10:05.440
It's very hot.

10:06.440 --> 10:08.000
So fussy.

10:08.000 --> 10:08.670
Okay, fine.

10:08.670 --> 10:10.070
I allow you to use a spoon.

10:11.460 --> 10:13.380
Revenge successful.

10:14.270 --> 10:15.870
Ms. Lin's going to show you

10:15.870 --> 10:18.360
how rough the world can be.

10:18.360 --> 10:20.360
So what are we doing this afternoon?

10:22.910 --> 10:25.670
Since you like
checking the time so much...

10:27.750 --> 10:28.910
I've got just the thing.

10:28.910 --> 10:29.710
What is it?

10:40.440 --> 10:42.320
According to the rules,
you're not allowed to check the time.

10:42.320 --> 10:43.440
Or else you lose.

10:45.960 --> 10:49.540
I'm going to drive you crazy
with your own discipline.

10:50.360 --> 10:52.420
Didn't you want to ride the duck boat?

10:52.550 --> 10:53.950
You won't check the time—

10:54.080 --> 10:55.880
aren't you afraid of missing it?

10:56.120 --> 10:56.840
No, I'm not.

10:57.390 --> 10:58.270
I don't care.

11:00.120 --> 11:02.250
Does it bother you not to know the time?

11:03.790 --> 11:04.510
Alright.

11:05.550 --> 11:07.480
I can let you in on a little secret.

11:10.240 --> 11:11.870
Actually,

11:11.870 --> 11:13.960
the wind can also help us keep time.

11:14.630 --> 11:16.320
The flow of those ripples

11:16.320 --> 11:17.600
is time itself.

11:18.600 --> 11:19.960
You could call it

11:19.960 --> 11:21.560
the "Ripple Timing Method."

11:25.750 --> 11:27.110
Tricking me again, huh?

11:27.670 --> 11:29.000
Yes, I am.

11:30.030 --> 11:31.150
You don't believe me?

11:31.150 --> 11:32.030
Of course not.

11:33.000 --> 11:33.870
I'll show you.

11:40.320 --> 11:42.600
Feel the ripples spreading out.

11:43.750 --> 11:45.120
Close your eyes.

11:45.750 --> 11:46.840
Each ring

11:46.840 --> 11:48.240
is about a second.

11:49.480 --> 11:50.630
The spread of ripples

11:50.630 --> 11:51.830
isn't linear.

12:00.000 --> 12:01.750
You know quite a lot.

12:02.440 --> 12:04.240
It's really not easy to fool you.

12:07.670 --> 12:08.440
Come on.

12:08.440 --> 12:09.240
You try it too.

12:24.720 --> 12:25.890
Imagine

12:26.200 --> 12:27.270
this lake

12:27.270 --> 12:28.240
is a canvas.

12:28.750 --> 12:31.000
The ripples are its brushstrokes.

12:31.970 --> 12:33.510
On this canvas,

12:33.510 --> 12:34.720
they paint it slowly.

12:35.670 --> 12:36.800
One second,

12:37.150 --> 12:38.490
two seconds,

12:38.790 --> 12:40.120
three seconds...

12:45.480 --> 12:47.390
Why'd he go quiet?

12:57.480 --> 12:58.880
The ripples

12:59.630 --> 13:01.990
should have passed the lotuses by now.

13:10.000 --> 13:10.800
That's right.

13:13.270 --> 13:15.110
After the lotuses,

13:15.440 --> 13:17.500
they should reach the fallen leaves.

13:17.960 --> 13:19.910
Under the leaves,

13:18.310 --> 13:23.460
♪ With the evening breeze
whispering in my ear ♪

13:19.910 --> 13:21.740
there are small fish.

13:22.240 --> 13:24.720
Three more rings spread outward,

13:24.460 --> 13:30.120
♪ Fireworks bloom across the sky ♪

13:24.720 --> 13:26.240
and then,

13:26.670 --> 13:28.530
they're about to reach the shore.

13:30.680 --> 13:33.770
♪ Shimmering in your eyes ♪

13:34.210 --> 13:39.610
♪ And spreading into
a gentle sea of stars ♪

13:42.680 --> 13:44.650
♪ Every night ♪

13:45.430 --> 13:47.400
♪ I reach for starlight ♪

13:47.970 --> 13:50.120
♪ Wandering through dreams with you ♪

13:50.930 --> 13:53.300
♪ I follow the beat of my heart ♪

13:53.970 --> 13:56.750
♪ Like dust floating in the air ♪

13:57.410 --> 13:59.420
♪ Because of your love ♪

14:00.100 --> 14:04.610
♪ I shine brilliantly ♪

14:02.510 --> 14:03.670
How was your nap?

14:10.150 --> 14:12.210
When I was little and wouldn't sleep,

14:12.390 --> 14:14.360
my grandpa would bring me to the lake

14:14.360 --> 14:16.960
and trick me
with this "Ripple Timing Method."

14:19.080 --> 14:20.230
I was tricking you.

14:20.440 --> 14:21.710
You just realized it?

14:22.960 --> 14:24.820
Your insomnia is pretty serious.

14:28.440 --> 14:29.600
I do have insomnia.

14:29.600 --> 14:30.440
So?

14:30.440 --> 14:32.490
So you should thank me even more.

14:32.520 --> 14:33.840
I repaid your cruelty with kindness

14:33.840 --> 14:36.770
and let you have
such a wonderful late afternoon nap.

14:39.240 --> 14:40.360
Coach Wang,

14:40.360 --> 14:41.390
you lost.

14:41.390 --> 14:42.590
You checked the time.

14:45.360 --> 14:46.510
You lost in the morning,

14:46.510 --> 14:47.390
and I lost this afternoon.

14:47.390 --> 14:48.190
So, it's a tie.

14:49.200 --> 14:50.240
Didn't we agree

14:50.440 --> 14:51.570
I'd only be the coach

14:51.670 --> 14:52.670
if you won?

14:53.440 --> 14:54.150
Fine.

14:54.720 --> 14:56.440
We'll see who has the last laugh.

14:56.440 --> 14:58.200
The day isn't over yet.

14:58.200 --> 15:00.460
I'll find a chance to turn things around.

15:06.550 --> 15:07.630
Didn't we agree

15:08.030 --> 15:09.170
I'd only be the coach

15:09.240 --> 15:10.240
if you won?

15:11.240 --> 15:12.930
Let me think about

15:12.950 --> 15:14.580
how to turn the tables.

15:14.970 --> 15:16.070
[Killing time] [Stay strong]

15:16.100 --> 15:17.700
[Stay strong] [Too hard]

15:17.720 --> 15:21.230
[No. 8 High School Team,
looking for a pro, come join the fight!]

15:18.870 --> 15:20.030
No. 8 High School Team,

15:20.030 --> 15:22.160
looking for a pro, come join the fight!

15:28.720 --> 15:30.360
When I said "today,"

15:30.720 --> 15:32.520
I didn't just mean this morning.

15:37.200 --> 15:38.480
Lin Lu,

15:38.540 --> 15:40.450
aren't you looking for a gaming pro?

15:40.450 --> 15:41.320
What a coincidence.

15:41.320 --> 15:42.750
I am one.

15:43.150 --> 15:44.270
Really?

15:44.720 --> 15:47.670
Games? Anyone with hands can play.

15:47.670 --> 15:48.870
Let's meet somewhere.

15:48.870 --> 15:50.200
I'll show you what I've got.

15:50.200 --> 15:51.200
But

15:51.200 --> 15:53.060
you'll have to make a deal with me.

15:53.490 --> 15:54.250
[Winfred]

15:54.280 --> 15:54.740
[Where are you?]

15:54.770 --> 15:55.460
[The neighborhood park.]

15:58.040 --> 16:05.390
[Slack Superstar]

15:58.390 --> 15:59.480
Coach Wang,

15:59.480 --> 16:01.120
today isn't over yet.

16:01.120 --> 16:02.390
I still have a chance

16:02.390 --> 16:03.670
to hit 800 kcal.

16:03.670 --> 16:04.720
Just you wait.

16:13.060 --> 16:14.790
[Cycling] [Average Pace: 9.3 km]

16:20.680 --> 16:22.130
[Coach Wang, today isn't over yet.]

16:22.150 --> 16:24.010
[I still have a chance to hit 800 kcal.
Just you wait.]

16:24.080 --> 16:25.910
Considering your fitness level,

16:25.910 --> 16:27.970
I'll let you cut back on the workload.

16:37.320 --> 16:38.390
Watch out, there's someone ahead.

16:38.390 --> 16:40.320
Run, run! Run to the safe zone.

16:43.480 --> 16:45.790
We're making it to the final circle.

16:45.790 --> 16:47.840
Only 23 players left.

16:48.150 --> 16:49.270
Northwest, northwest, northwest.

16:49.270 --> 16:50.950
Enemy at 330 degrees.

16:51.440 --> 16:52.200
Ms. Lin,

16:52.600 --> 16:54.440
what do you think Coach would do

16:54.440 --> 16:55.240
if he found out you were cheating?

16:55.240 --> 16:56.120
So what?

16:56.120 --> 16:57.750
Winning is all that matters.

16:57.750 --> 16:59.150
Who cares if he finds out?

17:03.720 --> 17:04.160
Ms. Lin.

17:04.160 --> 17:05.310
Oh no, oh no!

17:05.310 --> 17:06.640
There's a car behind us.

17:07.790 --> 17:08.700
Hide, hide.

17:08.720 --> 17:09.880
Hide, hide.

17:09.880 --> 17:11.000
Yes.

17:13.960 --> 17:14.960
Up ahead, up ahead.

17:14.960 --> 17:16.349
There's loot in front.

17:17.109 --> 17:18.720
Yeah, Spetsnaz Helmet.

17:26.440 --> 17:28.240
Ms. Lin, behind you.

17:28.240 --> 17:29.480
Thank you, Ms. Lin!

17:29.480 --> 17:30.240
You're so good,

17:30.240 --> 17:31.000
Ms. Lin!

17:55.400 --> 17:56.660
You cheated in our bet.

17:57.030 --> 17:57.920
Miss Landlady.

17:59.550 --> 18:00.350
You lost.

18:15.240 --> 18:17.070
I actually got caught.

18:22.280 --> 18:23.210
[Loves spicy food; hates coriander]

18:23.230 --> 18:24.250
[Bad at sports; can't ride a bike]

18:26.150 --> 18:27.350
[Loves spicy food; hates coriander]

18:27.370 --> 18:28.630
[Bad at sports; can't ride a bike]

18:34.840 --> 18:38.470
[Highly competitive; doesn't follow rules]

18:44.460 --> 18:51.810
[Spade Q—Lin Wanxing]

18:49.000 --> 18:50.640
She clearly matches

18:50.640 --> 18:52.440
almost every item on the list...

18:56.500 --> 18:58.840
♪ Two souls alike ♪

19:00.370 --> 19:02.710
♪ In the silent gravity ♪

19:04.400 --> 19:06.020
But why do I have

19:04.500 --> 19:06.850
♪ Cure my heart ♪

19:06.240 --> 19:07.830
this strange feeling...

19:07.280 --> 19:10.020
♪ With every part of you ♪

19:09.160 --> 19:10.490
Could she not be the one?

19:11.680 --> 19:13.130
That man is a scammer.

19:12.430 --> 19:14.580
♪ Our words flow ♪

19:13.310 --> 19:14.240
You're probably the only teacher

19:14.240 --> 19:15.440
around here.

19:15.910 --> 19:18.210
♪ Like a gentle stream ♪

19:16.310 --> 19:17.920
This isn't part of my job.

19:18.720 --> 19:20.440
This is the first lesson for you—

19:20.230 --> 19:22.830
♪ They glow like fireflies ♪

19:21.110 --> 19:22.840
obey the referee's decisions.

19:23.070 --> 19:25.800
♪ Inside of a silky dream ♪

19:23.110 --> 19:24.030
Never mind.

19:24.030 --> 19:25.750
We're just going through
the motions anyway.

19:25.750 --> 19:26.950
I'll waive your rent.

19:27.350 --> 19:29.640
I'll waive it as long as you coach them.

19:27.800 --> 19:33.850
♪ We talked the whole night, breeze away ♪

19:30.000 --> 19:31.480
I played a bit of a trick on you,

19:31.480 --> 19:33.350
but my wish for you to be the coach

19:33.350 --> 19:34.240
is genuine.

19:35.730 --> 19:37.620
♪ Together we set out on a long journey ♪

19:35.750 --> 19:37.510
Who is she, really?

19:38.030 --> 19:41.720
♪ The endless journey ♪

19:40.440 --> 19:41.720
Coach Wang,

19:41.720 --> 19:42.880
are you home?

19:51.680 --> 19:53.000
A bet is a bet,

19:53.000 --> 19:54.070
Miss Landlady.

19:54.960 --> 19:56.270
But I still want to

19:56.270 --> 19:57.880
make a last-ditch effort.

19:59.350 --> 20:00.400
How?

20:00.400 --> 20:01.790
By offering you a fair trade.

20:01.790 --> 20:03.520
How long have you had insomnia?

20:04.270 --> 20:05.440
I have it all figured out.

20:05.440 --> 20:06.160
How about this?

20:06.160 --> 20:07.920
You come coach
at Hongjing No. 8 High School,

20:07.920 --> 20:09.980
and I'll help you with your insomnia.

20:12.590 --> 20:13.510
I swear

20:13.510 --> 20:14.590
I'll make you sleep

20:14.590 --> 20:16.030
deeply and peacefully.

20:16.720 --> 20:18.310
Lifestyle habits alone

20:18.480 --> 20:20.030
aren't enough to prove anything.

20:20.030 --> 20:22.000
Perhaps through more interaction,

20:22.000 --> 20:23.730
I can uncover more of the truth.

20:24.680 --> 20:25.880
Your proposal...

20:26.350 --> 20:27.350
has persuaded me.

20:29.550 --> 20:30.750
So,

20:31.310 --> 20:32.200
you agree?

20:33.590 --> 20:34.270
Deal.

20:36.550 --> 20:38.510
So the strong really do have

20:38.510 --> 20:40.070
a psychological edge.

20:40.070 --> 20:41.000
What do you mean?

20:41.200 --> 20:43.440
It's a concept in psychology:

20:43.440 --> 20:45.440
the psychological edge of the strong.

20:45.440 --> 20:48.000
You've always been
the stronger one in your life.

20:48.000 --> 20:48.920
A truly strong person

20:48.920 --> 20:51.510
doesn't need to
crush the weak to prove their strength.

20:51.510 --> 20:52.070
On the contrary,

20:52.070 --> 20:53.200
they demonstrate

20:53.200 --> 20:55.000
control through yielding.

20:55.000 --> 20:56.270
So, I thought

20:56.270 --> 20:57.440
I still had a chance.

20:57.440 --> 21:00.350
Coach Wang, I'm really not trying to
manipulate you.

21:00.350 --> 21:01.270
Think about it.

21:01.270 --> 21:01.920
Actually,

21:01.920 --> 21:03.920
the moment you made eye contact
with those kids yesterday,

21:03.920 --> 21:05.640
you'd already made your decision,

21:05.640 --> 21:06.270
right?

21:08.640 --> 21:10.260
Thank you, Coach Wang Fa.

21:10.400 --> 21:13.530
Welcome to the Hongjing No. 8 High School
football team.

21:30.510 --> 21:31.510
Fu Xinshu, Fu Xinshu,

21:31.510 --> 21:33.840
help me create a group chat with everyone.

21:34.070 --> 21:35.790
Hello, Ms. Dan, I'm here again.

21:35.790 --> 21:36.750
You're here? Have a seat inside.

21:36.750 --> 21:38.110
-Come in and find a table.
-Come in.

21:38.110 --> 21:39.270
-Feiyang, go easy on the chili.
-Help yourself.

21:39.270 --> 21:39.720
No problem.

21:39.720 --> 21:41.440
Auntie, please
keep an eye on him for me, thanks.

21:41.440 --> 21:43.270
-Sure.
-Come help me with this.

21:44.350 --> 21:45.610
Uncle, let me help you.

21:48.350 --> 21:49.510
I fried these myself!

21:49.510 --> 21:51.880
-You made them yourself?
-You fried these?

21:51.880 --> 21:53.110
-Then I'm gonna pass.
-Are you sure?

21:53.110 --> 21:54.350
Let me be the guinea pig.

21:54.350 --> 21:56.150
I c-can't eat it, not even a bite.

21:56.510 --> 21:57.640
-Stop fussing around.
-Hurry up and eat.

21:57.640 --> 21:59.640
Feiyang, they're actually pretty good!

21:59.640 --> 22:01.880
Of course. My cooking speaks for itself.

22:01.880 --> 22:03.000
Let me try. Let me try.

22:03.000 --> 22:04.830
Are you complimenting him
or making fun of him?

22:04.830 --> 22:06.090
You ate the spicy ones.

22:06.750 --> 22:07.550
I saw that too.

22:07.550 --> 22:08.440
Delicious. Delicious.

22:08.160 --> 22:09.860
[Group Chat]

22:08.680 --> 22:09.680
Yes, Ginger Duck.

22:10.040 --> 22:11.350
I didn't overuse that trick, did I?

22:11.350 --> 22:12.590
Didn't I teach you already?

22:12.590 --> 22:14.310
Fu started a new group chat.

22:14.310 --> 22:15.580
Everyone, take a look.

22:15.600 --> 22:17.400
Ms. Lin joined too.

22:17.060 --> 22:18.510
[Little Savage Tribe]

22:17.400 --> 22:19.570
She even renamed the group
Little Savage Tribe.

22:19.570 --> 22:21.190
What's "Little Savage" supposed to mean?

22:21.190 --> 22:22.630
[Little Savage Tribe]

22:21.480 --> 22:22.750
I hereby announce

22:22.750 --> 22:24.200
-you have a coach now.
-Wait.

22:24.200 --> 22:25.000
Everyone, assemble tomorrow

22:25.000 --> 22:26.350
and start training.

22:26.350 --> 22:27.400
Really?

22:27.400 --> 22:29.110
Former Nanton FC Youth Academy Coach?

22:29.110 --> 22:29.880
Nanton!

22:29.880 --> 22:30.790
No way.

22:31.070 --> 22:32.150
I'm not seeing things, am I?

22:32.150 --> 22:33.750
-Really?
-Are you joking?

22:33.750 --> 22:36.420
A former Nanton youth coach
is going to train us?

22:36.590 --> 22:38.830
Ms. Lin, this joke isn't funny.

22:41.310 --> 22:42.920
It's not a joke.

22:42.920 --> 22:43.880
I'll have your coach come out

22:43.880 --> 22:45.210
and confirm it himself.

22:47.030 --> 22:48.240
I'm the real deal.

22:49.240 --> 22:51.920
Ms. Lin, did you kidnap him or something?

22:55.440 --> 22:58.650
Either leave the group
or treat everyone to milk tea.

22:58.670 --> 23:00.590
Welcome, Coach.

23:00.750 --> 23:01.440
+1.

23:01.440 --> 23:02.440
+1!

23:02.790 --> 23:03.750
+1.

23:04.400 --> 23:05.400
+1.

23:05.400 --> 23:06.160
+1.

23:06.640 --> 23:07.440
+1.

23:08.010 --> 23:09.580
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

23:09.830 --> 23:10.640
+1.

23:11.160 --> 23:11.960
+1.

23:12.750 --> 23:13.110
+1.

23:13.110 --> 23:14.400
-Keep your word.
-+1.

23:14.400 --> 23:16.930
-Remember to come to training tomorrow.
-+1.

23:17.270 --> 23:18.920
-See you guys there.
-+1.

23:42.350 --> 23:44.000
This one again.

23:51.950 --> 23:54.800
[Hongjing No. 8 High School
Football Team Roster]

23:52.240 --> 23:53.110
Coach Wang,

23:53.110 --> 23:55.070
here's the file with player profiles.

23:55.070 --> 23:56.200
See you tomorrow.

23:56.310 --> 23:57.780
[Hongjing No. 8 High School
Football Team Roster]

24:01.400 --> 24:02.160
Okay.

24:09.550 --> 24:11.880
Why name it the "Little Savage Tribe"?

24:19.830 --> 24:21.240
No reason.

24:21.240 --> 24:22.440
It's just a nickname.

24:34.200 --> 24:36.110
You prickly QR Code.

24:36.110 --> 24:37.750
I'm counting on you from here.

24:37.750 --> 24:39.640
Do your best.

24:47.920 --> 24:48.640
You're back from work.

24:48.640 --> 24:50.200
Why are you still at it this late?

24:50.200 --> 24:50.750
Let me help.

24:50.750 --> 24:52.030
I collected quite a bit today.

24:52.030 --> 24:52.880
Sort them out now,

24:52.880 --> 24:54.790
and I can sell them
first thing tomorrow morning.

24:54.790 --> 24:55.830
-Here.
-Come on.

24:57.960 --> 24:58.790
Move your leg.

25:01.960 --> 25:03.070
Okay. Okay.

25:04.510 --> 25:05.750
Right, just pile it up here.

25:05.750 --> 25:06.440
All done, Grandma.

25:06.440 --> 25:08.160
You've worked hard. Go back and rest.

25:08.160 --> 25:10.750
You've worked hard, Grandma.

25:08.290 --> 25:12.420
[Serenity Leads to Vision]

25:10.750 --> 25:12.350
Okay, go to sleep early too.

25:12.350 --> 25:13.510
Get up early tomorrow.

25:13.510 --> 25:15.550
I'll make you red bean porridge.

25:15.550 --> 25:16.790
Okay, Grandma.

25:16.790 --> 25:17.480
Good night.

25:33.890 --> 25:35.090
[Mom, we tied with
Ning'an Experimental School.]

25:34.750 --> 25:35.810
Congratulations.

25:37.750 --> 25:39.550
Xinshu, there's one more thing.

25:39.790 --> 25:41.270
Remember I told you

25:41.270 --> 25:43.350
I've been feeling unwell lately?

25:43.350 --> 25:45.950
I've booked an appointment
with a specialist.

25:46.440 --> 25:47.840
Has it gotten worse, Mom?

25:48.960 --> 25:50.750
What day is your appointment?

25:50.790 --> 25:52.450
Do you want me to come with you?

25:54.960 --> 25:55.690
No need.

25:56.240 --> 25:58.370
It's just that I'm a bit tight on money.

26:00.350 --> 26:02.980
[Transfer amount: 3,000]

26:04.750 --> 26:07.000
Mom, your health comes first.

26:07.000 --> 26:09.160
If you're short on money, just tell me.

26:13.900 --> 26:14.720
[Qiuhua Community Health Center]

26:14.750 --> 26:15.900
[Hongjing City Bus Card Top-up Center]

26:15.920 --> 26:17.490
[Guan Minjie]

26:20.930 --> 26:21.160
[Qiuhua Community Health Center]

26:21.190 --> 26:21.530
[Guan Minjie]

26:21.600 --> 26:23.060
[Mom, we tied with
Ning'an Experimental School.]

26:27.240 --> 26:28.300
Congratulations.

26:33.510 --> 26:34.680
Congratulations.

26:37.400 --> 26:38.680
Congratulations.

26:45.310 --> 26:46.640
When do you think Coach will get here?

26:45.640 --> 26:46.510
[Warmly welcoming Coach Wang Fa]

26:46.540 --> 26:47.480
[to join the Hongjing No. 8 High School
Football Team]

26:46.640 --> 26:48.070
I can't wait.

26:48.070 --> 26:48.880
I can't believe something this good

26:48.880 --> 26:50.310
actually happened to us.

26:54.310 --> 26:55.370
You hit me for real?

26:57.510 --> 26:58.570
-Come on.
-Go away.

27:00.070 --> 27:01.110
What time is it?

27:01.110 --> 27:02.550
Ten to three.

27:02.920 --> 27:04.350
That's the third time
you've asked in 10 minutes.

27:04.350 --> 27:05.350
Come on, bro.

27:05.880 --> 27:06.830
Guys,

27:06.830 --> 27:08.440
if he's even one minute late,

27:08.440 --> 27:09.540
we're leaving.

27:09.830 --> 27:11.350
We agreed to meet at three.

27:12.270 --> 27:14.270
Even I know to arrive early
for something like this.

27:14.270 --> 27:16.200
He's obviously not being sincere.

27:16.230 --> 27:18.110
Maybe he never intended to come at all.

27:18.110 --> 27:19.270
Just messing with us.

27:19.270 --> 27:20.680
True.

27:23.110 --> 27:24.830
Qin Ao, it's not time yet.

27:24.830 --> 27:26.920
-A former Nanton youth coach.
-What?

27:26.920 --> 27:29.110
Weren't you so excited
you couldn't sleep last night?

27:29.110 --> 27:30.830
I'm just going to buy a soda.

27:31.440 --> 27:32.110
What?

27:33.510 --> 27:34.510
I'm not late, am I?

27:38.530 --> 27:39.310
He's really here.

27:39.310 --> 27:39.920
Everyone, over here.

27:39.920 --> 27:40.570
Line up.

27:41.180 --> 27:42.000
Go, go, go.

27:42.000 --> 27:43.130
Hurry, hurry.

27:43.720 --> 27:44.720
Line up, line up.

27:49.640 --> 27:51.160
Come on, line up.

27:52.310 --> 27:52.960
Hurry up.

27:56.790 --> 27:57.680
I'm Wang Fa.

28:04.400 --> 28:05.750
Midfielder Fu Xinshu.

28:05.750 --> 28:06.590
Hello, Coach.

28:10.240 --> 28:11.500
Forward Chen Jianghe.

28:13.720 --> 28:14.720
Forward Qin Ao.

28:18.830 --> 28:19.350
Here.

28:22.510 --> 28:23.550
Defender Lin Lu.

28:23.550 --> 28:24.200
Here.

28:24.720 --> 28:25.830
Defender Qi Liang.

28:25.830 --> 28:26.550
Here.

28:26.750 --> 28:27.590
Defender Yu Ming.

28:27.590 --> 28:28.390
Hello, Coach.

28:28.590 --> 28:29.540
Defender Zheng Feiyang.

28:29.540 --> 28:30.030
Here.

28:30.590 --> 28:31.550
Midfielder Zheng Ren.

28:31.550 --> 28:32.430
Hello, Coach.

28:32.640 --> 28:33.750
Midfielder Zhi Hui.

28:33.750 --> 28:34.510
Hello, Coach.

28:34.510 --> 28:35.510
Goalkeeper Feng Suo.

28:35.510 --> 28:36.350
Hello, Coach.

28:38.750 --> 28:40.920
One player, Chen Weidong, is absent.

28:40.920 --> 28:42.850
He's training with the track team.

28:44.350 --> 28:46.160
As for our future training schedule,

28:46.160 --> 28:48.000
I'll coach the team
from 3:00 to 5:00 every afternoon.

28:48.000 --> 28:49.270
If anything changes,

28:49.270 --> 28:50.640
Ms. Lin will notify you.

28:52.880 --> 28:54.070
Alright, boys.

28:55.920 --> 28:57.920
Now that Coach Wang Fa has joined us,

28:57.920 --> 29:00.680
I believe our Hongjing No. 8 High School
football team

29:00.680 --> 29:03.200
will rise again, grow stronger,

29:03.200 --> 29:04.480
and reach new heights of glory.

29:04.480 --> 29:05.790
Yeah! Great!

29:05.790 --> 29:07.960
-Thank you, Coach.
-Thank you, Coach.

29:07.960 --> 29:10.360
Ms. Lin, your idioms are quite old-school.

29:10.640 --> 29:13.240
Does the great coach
have anything else to say?

29:14.680 --> 29:16.210
I'm just a temporary coach,

29:16.480 --> 29:18.010
filling in for a short time.

29:24.310 --> 29:25.240
That's still great.

29:25.240 --> 29:26.400
Even just half an hour of your coaching

29:26.400 --> 29:27.240
would be worth it for us,

29:27.240 --> 29:27.750
right?

29:29.480 --> 29:30.270
Then...

29:30.760 --> 29:31.400
let's get to training.

29:31.400 --> 29:32.680
-Let's go.
-Wait.

29:33.830 --> 29:35.290
Shouldn't we do something

29:35.650 --> 29:36.850
to mark the occasion?

29:37.550 --> 29:38.480
What do you mean?

29:43.590 --> 29:44.960
Sign a football?

29:44.960 --> 29:46.440
When we all become famous someday,

29:46.440 --> 29:47.790
this'll be priceless.

29:47.790 --> 29:48.880
Captain, you go first.

29:48.880 --> 29:50.160
-I'll go first then.
-Okay.

29:50.160 --> 29:51.560
-I'll go first.
-Come on.

29:56.610 --> 29:58.150
[Fu Xinshu]

29:58.680 --> 29:59.480
Here.

29:58.680 --> 30:01.740
♪ Who isn't going through nights
of darkness and confusion ♪

29:59.480 --> 30:00.510
Me first, me first.

30:00.090 --> 30:01.040
[Zheng Ren]

30:02.520 --> 30:06.120
♪ Stumbling, covered in wounds,
losing direction ♪

30:03.120 --> 30:04.270
[Feng Suo]

30:06.520 --> 30:12.520
♪ Wandering alone,
gaining strength through pain ♪

30:08.140 --> 30:09.660
[Zheng]

30:09.920 --> 30:13.070
Now it really feels like a football team
with star players.

30:13.070 --> 30:13.680
Totally.

30:14.800 --> 30:17.470
♪ Riding the wind,
chasing an unknown horizon ♪

30:15.030 --> 30:15.960
My turn, my turn.

30:18.660 --> 30:22.490
♪ Looking up,
dreaming side by side of great ideals ♪

30:18.780 --> 30:20.800
[Lin Lu]

30:21.940 --> 30:23.710
Boss, sign next to mine.

30:22.890 --> 30:28.990
♪ The vast world
awaits youth to arrive ♪

30:25.240 --> 30:26.920
Don't be so quick to forget.

30:28.920 --> 30:29.880
It's for Fu's sake.

30:29.560 --> 30:32.910
♪ If facing every storm is ♪

30:29.880 --> 30:31.610
I'll just scribble something.

30:33.320 --> 30:36.550
♪ What it takes to grow ♪

30:36.550 --> 30:38.000
You're the one taking it most seriously.

30:37.410 --> 30:40.150
♪ I will stubbornly
go against the current ♪

30:37.800 --> 30:39.860
[Qin]

30:40.950 --> 30:43.800
♪ And let myself go wild ♪

30:42.760 --> 30:44.950
[Qin Ao]

30:44.660 --> 30:48.070
♪ No matter how long the road ahead ♪

30:45.830 --> 30:47.200
It's really big.

30:48.880 --> 30:51.700
♪ Nothing can stop me ♪

30:49.720 --> 30:51.100
Quit pretending, dude.

30:51.350 --> 30:51.960
Here, pen.

30:52.440 --> 30:53.400
So annoying.

30:52.980 --> 30:54.160
♪ Break through every haze of doubt ♪

30:54.550 --> 30:55.520
Look at his goofy face.

30:54.900 --> 30:56.460
♪ Chase the light within me ♪

30:57.470 --> 30:59.950
♪ Strong wings grow through the storm ♪

31:00.670 --> 31:04.040
♪ Even if no one cheers ♪

31:04.580 --> 31:06.970
♪ I'll keep fighting my way through ♪

31:06.510 --> 31:07.200
Coach.

31:08.630 --> 31:10.560
♪ On a deserted battlefield ♪

31:11.120 --> 31:12.700
♪ I grow stronger
with a resounding voice ♪

31:12.830 --> 31:14.810
It's not like
you're signing away your soul.

31:13.100 --> 31:16.410
♪ I'll take every scar ♪

31:15.070 --> 31:17.830
Just a sweet memento
of our friendly cooperation.

31:16.870 --> 31:20.180
♪ As my badge of honor ♪

31:33.540 --> 31:36.890
♪ If facing every storm is ♪

31:37.290 --> 31:40.530
♪ What it takes to grow ♪

31:41.380 --> 31:44.120
♪ I will stubbornly
go against the current ♪

31:44.920 --> 31:47.650
♪ And let myself go wild ♪

31:46.200 --> 31:46.960
Alright, boys.

31:46.960 --> 31:47.640
It's about time.

31:47.640 --> 31:49.160
Hurry up and go to training.

31:48.640 --> 31:52.040
♪ No matter how long the road ahead ♪

31:50.190 --> 31:51.270
[Feng Suo] [Qin Ao]

31:52.850 --> 31:55.680
♪ Nothing can stop me ♪

31:52.880 --> 31:53.480
Okay.

31:53.480 --> 31:54.610
Everyone, let's go train.

31:54.610 --> 31:56.050
-Okay, okay.
-Let's go.

31:56.950 --> 31:58.140
♪ Break through every haze of doubt ♪

31:58.880 --> 32:00.430
♪ Chase the light within me ♪

32:01.440 --> 32:03.920
♪ Strong wings grow through the storm ♪

32:02.680 --> 32:03.640
Coach Wang Fa.

32:04.640 --> 32:08.010
♪ Even if no one cheers ♪

32:05.350 --> 32:06.400
Your whistle.

32:08.560 --> 32:10.950
♪ I'll keep fighting my way through ♪

32:12.610 --> 32:14.540
♪ On a deserted battlefield ♪

32:15.090 --> 32:16.670
♪ I grow stronger
with a resounding voice ♪

32:16.340 --> 32:20.330
[Feng Suo]

32:17.080 --> 32:20.390
♪ I'll take every scar ♪

32:20.840 --> 32:24.160
♪ As my badge of honor ♪

32:28.270 --> 32:28.830
Coach,

32:29.200 --> 32:30.550
what are we training today?

32:30.550 --> 32:31.440
Quick short passing combos,

32:31.440 --> 32:33.370
or Nanton's signature high press?

32:37.440 --> 32:39.920
Hurry up and give the orders.

32:39.920 --> 32:41.480
They're all waiting.

32:46.960 --> 32:47.960
Captain, lead the team.

32:47.960 --> 32:48.590
Run laps.

32:48.960 --> 32:49.670
Run laps?

32:51.030 --> 32:51.640
Okay.

32:52.070 --> 32:54.070
Everyone, gather by the edge of the field.

32:54.070 --> 32:54.510
Let's go!

32:54.510 --> 32:55.370
Let's go, Boss.

32:57.590 --> 32:58.830
Sorry, I'm late.

33:00.030 --> 33:00.550
Fall in.

33:01.110 --> 33:02.450
Quick march.

33:10.880 --> 33:13.090
I wonder what he's up to.

33:59.110 --> 34:01.440
Fu, that should be enough running, right?

34:02.270 --> 34:03.480
It should be.

34:04.410 --> 34:05.350
Okay, everyone, stop for a second.

34:05.350 --> 34:05.830
Alright.

34:05.830 --> 34:06.770
I'll go ask.

34:09.840 --> 34:10.510
Coach,

34:10.710 --> 34:12.630
we've finished three warm-up laps.

34:12.630 --> 34:13.550
So what's next?

34:13.550 --> 34:14.350
Keep running.

34:19.110 --> 34:19.710
Okay.

34:21.590 --> 34:22.480
Keep running!

34:23.110 --> 34:25.280
Looks like he's playing mind games.

34:25.280 --> 34:26.010
Come on, let's go.

34:26.010 --> 34:27.030
Go, go, go!

34:27.030 --> 34:28.070
Why?

34:28.070 --> 34:29.929
-Keep running.
-Keep up, keep up!

34:36.800 --> 34:38.920
I never get tired of this snack.

34:47.429 --> 34:48.429
Don't mind if I do.

34:48.690 --> 34:49.600
Not again.

34:55.400 --> 34:58.230
You took the whole bag
like it was only natural?

35:02.030 --> 35:03.090
Playing dumb, huh?

35:03.230 --> 35:04.830
Can we talk about something?

35:06.360 --> 35:07.030
Go ahead.

35:10.360 --> 35:11.750
A bag of snacks—

35:11.770 --> 35:13.120
my snacks—

35:13.230 --> 35:15.000
I should get two-thirds,

35:15.000 --> 35:16.440
and you get one-third.

35:16.440 --> 35:18.440
So much for "friendly cooperation", huh?

35:18.440 --> 35:19.900
Using my words against me?

35:22.510 --> 35:23.490
Alright.

35:23.510 --> 35:25.240
Half and half, then.

35:25.360 --> 35:27.490
I'll show my sincerity with fairness.

35:27.630 --> 35:28.690
Pour them out then.

35:29.110 --> 35:29.770
I'll count.

35:30.320 --> 35:32.520
Seriously? What's wrong with this guy?

35:33.590 --> 35:34.250
I poured...

35:34.710 --> 35:35.510
Thanks.

35:35.510 --> 35:36.770
I feel your sincerity.

35:37.030 --> 35:38.960
I'm so pissed.

35:41.320 --> 35:42.640
Eat, eat.

35:43.000 --> 35:45.230
Hope you'll be a little nicer to the kids.

35:45.230 --> 35:46.510
I'll consider it your fee.

35:46.510 --> 35:47.320
Formation.

35:47.320 --> 35:48.280
Why are we still running?

35:48.280 --> 35:50.070
How many laps have we done?

35:50.070 --> 35:51.630
I'm exhausted.

36:06.400 --> 36:08.110
Wen Chengye?

36:09.280 --> 36:11.190
What's he doing here?

36:12.510 --> 36:13.630
I can't run anymore.

36:13.630 --> 36:15.330
-Stop talking. Focus on your breathing.
-Fu.

36:15.330 --> 36:17.450
Fu, do we still need to run?

36:17.480 --> 36:18.440
Why don't you go ask?

36:18.440 --> 36:19.630
-Yeah. Go.
-Yeah. Go ask him.

36:19.630 --> 36:20.550
Go ask quickly.

36:20.550 --> 36:21.810
Okay, everyone, stop.

36:22.110 --> 36:22.970
I'll ask again.

36:27.000 --> 36:29.150
Coach, we've done 10 laps already.

36:29.590 --> 36:30.710
Do we keep going?

36:31.030 --> 36:31.550
Yes.

36:36.440 --> 36:37.510
Still running?

36:39.630 --> 36:41.110
Should I ask?

36:42.800 --> 36:44.110
-Alright.
-Forget it.

36:44.130 --> 36:45.390
I'm just a layman here.

36:45.510 --> 36:47.530
I'd better trust Coach on this.

36:49.630 --> 36:50.480
Guys!

36:51.320 --> 36:52.190
Keep running.

36:53.280 --> 36:54.360
More laps?

36:54.360 --> 36:55.330
Hang in there.

36:55.510 --> 36:56.800
-Come on! Come on!
-I can't run anymore.

36:56.800 --> 36:58.360
-My legs are about to cramp.
-Let's go.

36:58.360 --> 37:00.190
Are they trying to kill us?

37:00.190 --> 37:01.840
-Feng Suo, keep up!
-No, I seriously can't run anymore!

37:01.840 --> 37:02.710
Hang in there!

37:13.960 --> 37:15.760
-Keep up.
-Just a little longer.

37:20.590 --> 37:21.760
Let's stop running.

37:22.800 --> 37:23.730
Keep up, come on.

37:24.230 --> 37:25.720
What lap are we on?

37:27.150 --> 37:28.000
Keep up, keep up.

37:28.000 --> 37:28.920
Hang in there.

37:33.960 --> 37:36.070
Will this ever end?
We've been running forever.

37:36.070 --> 37:37.330
I'm about to drop dead.

37:37.710 --> 37:38.840
How long has it been?

37:38.840 --> 37:40.150
Still going?

37:40.920 --> 37:42.510
I can see they're hitting their limit.

37:42.510 --> 37:43.880
How much longer are we supposed to run?

37:43.880 --> 37:45.630
Hang in there, boys.

37:46.150 --> 37:47.070
Captain, I need a break.

37:47.070 --> 37:48.870
-No stopping.
-Let me walk a bit.

37:49.110 --> 37:49.710
Go.

37:51.030 --> 37:52.290
-No.
-Keep up. Keep up.

37:56.360 --> 37:58.220
What exactly are you trying to do?

37:59.590 --> 38:00.760
Nothing.

38:01.480 --> 38:03.280
Then is that all we're training today?

38:03.280 --> 38:04.230
Yes.

38:04.230 --> 38:05.880
What's the point of long-distance jogging?

38:05.880 --> 38:07.480
It won't improve our fitness at all.

38:07.480 --> 38:08.800
-Yeah.
-Exactly.

38:09.510 --> 38:10.510
Long-distance jogging

38:10.510 --> 38:12.960
will also affect
your speed and explosiveness.

38:12.960 --> 38:15.060
So he's using reverse psychology.

38:16.920 --> 38:18.400
You never wanted to
coach us in the first place, did you?

38:18.400 --> 38:20.030
Is this what Nanton's
advanced training is—

38:20.030 --> 38:20.880
just making players run?

38:20.880 --> 38:21.880
Exactly.

38:21.880 --> 38:22.710
Are you kidding us?

38:22.710 --> 38:24.280
I thought we were shooting a movie—

38:24.280 --> 38:25.440
running lap after lap.

38:25.440 --> 38:26.890
Playing us for fools, huh?

38:26.890 --> 38:27.600
Fine.

38:27.670 --> 38:28.360
We're out!

38:34.190 --> 38:35.030
Coach,

38:35.030 --> 38:36.760
you never wanted to
train us in the first place,

38:36.760 --> 38:37.510
did you?

38:38.800 --> 38:40.400
So you think this is on me too?

38:40.480 --> 38:41.740
Why bother asking him?

38:41.920 --> 38:43.190
Isn't it obvious?

38:43.190 --> 38:45.510
We're not good enough
for a coach from Nanton.

38:45.510 --> 38:46.480
Do you get it now?

38:57.480 --> 38:58.800
Don't look at me.

38:59.000 --> 39:00.920
You'll have to work out the coordination

39:00.920 --> 39:02.560
with your coach on your own.

39:28.630 --> 39:29.840
I told you so.

39:29.860 --> 39:31.120
They were never worth trusting.

39:31.120 --> 39:32.100
Reality just slapped you in the face, huh?

39:32.100 --> 39:33.920
A coach from Nanton's youth academy—
why would someone like him

39:33.920 --> 39:35.780
ever think we're worth coaching?

39:35.840 --> 39:36.510
You talk too much.

39:36.510 --> 39:37.840
Would it kill you to say less?

39:37.840 --> 39:38.480
Yes!

39:40.590 --> 39:41.840
-Fu.
-Fu.

39:42.190 --> 39:43.360
-See?
-Fu!

39:44.320 --> 39:45.880
Fu, where are you going?

39:46.590 --> 39:47.920
Fu Xinshu!

39:47.920 --> 39:49.150
What's going on?

39:49.150 --> 39:50.590
Why did Fu leave?

39:54.840 --> 39:55.840
Ms. Lin.

39:56.480 --> 39:57.280
What's wrong?

39:57.800 --> 39:59.930
Did Coach Wang leave any explanation?

40:04.360 --> 40:07.360
And you didn't ask us to
go back and continue training.

40:09.350 --> 40:10.880
That was your own decision.

40:11.670 --> 40:13.270
I have no right to interfere.

40:16.710 --> 40:17.480
That's true.

40:18.400 --> 40:19.660
I was overthinking it.

40:20.840 --> 40:22.840
You really don't need to interfere.

40:26.630 --> 40:28.090
You, just like Coach Wang,

40:28.960 --> 40:29.800
must think

40:29.800 --> 40:31.060
we're not good enough.

40:33.190 --> 40:34.400
It's not like that.

40:34.400 --> 40:36.400
Coach Wang didn't sign the football,

40:36.400 --> 40:37.530
and neither did you.

40:37.920 --> 40:38.800
Why?

40:41.110 --> 40:42.300
That's because...

40:42.510 --> 40:44.480
I'm just a team supervisor.

40:45.230 --> 40:46.690
Is that really the reason?

40:47.150 --> 40:47.840
Isn't it because,

40:47.840 --> 40:49.570
in your and Coach Wang's minds,

40:49.840 --> 40:51.960
the football team has always just been us,

40:51.960 --> 40:54.290
and there's no need
for you to be part of it?

41:04.440 --> 41:05.230
Makes sense.

41:06.840 --> 41:08.360
How we play,

41:10.280 --> 41:11.540
whether we win or lose,

41:12.000 --> 41:14.260
has nothing to do with you anyway, right?

41:17.840 --> 41:19.440
Sorry to bother you, Ms. Lin.

41:42.670 --> 41:44.350
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

41:45.290 --> 41:46.780
♪ Because you're with me ♪

41:49.530 --> 41:51.060
♪ The light shimmers ♪

41:52.310 --> 41:53.620
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

41:55.250 --> 41:56.390
♪ Running towards you ♪

41:57.180 --> 41:58.440
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪

42:02.210 --> 42:03.510
♪ Walk side by side ♪

42:04.000 --> 42:06.130
♪ Become ourselves ♪

42:08.320 --> 42:09.550
♪ Amid the storm ♪
